author: @heimeshc.2039
text: I remember listening to Self-portrait with my girlfriend for the first time, not knowing what we were walking into, we instantly fell in love with his art, his being. We used to listen to EXO a little before, but after this album, we explored and explored, there was no end to the godly art these brilliant men had put out there. We binge watched their content so frequently, we watched all their shows that we could. God. This hits hard. After waiting for so long, he is finally back. It takes me down this memory lane, the sweetest I've ever had. I couldn't be happier. Man.. it's too much. hah. Only if he could somehow know how much we truly love him.
